一个没有人通过投机取巧 和非法手段获利的社会
A society without those who gain by cheating and breaking the law.

711
00:52:15,960 --> 00:52:17,500
一个罪犯…
A society where a criminal…

712
00:52:19,210 --> 00:52:22,260
为其罪行付出代价的社会
pays the price of their wrongdoings."

713
00:52:26,510 --> 00:52:29,350
你教导我说这才是一个正义的社会
You taught me that is what a just society looks like.

714
00:52:32,220 --> 00:52:33,350
智勋
Jihun.

715
00:52:34,730 --> 00:52:38,060
我当上总理后 一定会让它实现
I will become the prime minister and make sure that happens.

716
00:52:38,150 --> 00:52:40,980
不 你不能
No, you can't.

717
00:52:42,070 --> 00:52:43,570
我会纠正过来
I will put things right.

718
00:52:54,370 --> 00:52:56,290
你愣着干吗 打声招呼啊
What are you doing? Introduce yourself.

719
00:52:59,290 --> 00:53:01,630
你好 我是千智勋检察官
Nice to meet you. I am Prosecutor Cheon Jihun.

720
00:53:01,710 --> 00:53:03,300
我们以前见过面吧
I believe we've met before.

721
00:53:04,340 --> 00:53:05,380
是吗 前辈
Have you met him already?

722
00:53:06,260 --> 00:53:09,510
他让我过来接受调查
He summoned me for an investigation.

723
00:53:11,430 --> 00:53:12,430
这是什么…
What are you…

724
00:53:12,930 --> 00:53:15,430
千检察官 你告诉他们吧
Mr. Cheon, why don't you tell them?

725
00:53:18,730 --> 00:53:21,940
是的 关于崔基泰案的秘密资金 我需要对他进行调查
Yes, I need to interview him in relation to Choi Kitae's slush fund.

726
00:53:22,070 --> 00:53:23,440
你疯了吗
Are you out of your mind?

727
00:53:23,940 --> 00:53:24,900
这是什么意思
What are you saying?

728
00:53:24,990 --> 00:53:26,110
没关系
It's fine.

729
00:53:27,400 --> 00:53:28,780
我会接受调查
I will heed the summon.

730
00:53:29,910 --> 00:53:33,870
我不能打击年轻检察官的调查意志
I shouldn't break the will of a young prosecutor.

731
00:53:39,420 --> 00:53:42,210
首尔中央地方检察厅
SEOUL CENTRAL DISTRICT PROSECUTORS' OFFICE

732
00:53:43,300 --> 00:53:44,760
智勋一个人可以吗
Will Jihun be okay alone?

733
00:53:45,460 --> 00:53:47,680
是智勋想要这样
That is what Jihun wants.

734
00:53:48,260 --> 00:53:51,510
我刚才看到他和金允燮候选人 之间的气氛很奇怪
From what I saw, things were weird between him and Candidate Kim Yoonsub.

735
00:53:52,100 --> 00:53:53,220
他们之间有什么事吗
Is there something going on?

736
00:53:53,430 --> 00:53:55,020
我去看看吧
I should stop by.

737
00:53:55,770 --> 00:53:56,770
民赫
Minhyeok.

738
00:53:58,690 --> 00:54:01,560
由他去吧 他肯定有自己的想法
Leave him alone. I'm sure he knows what he's doing.

739
00:54:14,330 --> 00:54:16,660
你第一次见到崔基泰代表是什么时候
When was the first time you met President Choi Kitae?

740
00:54:17,410 --> 00:54:19,330
应该是在三年前
It was probably three years ago.

741
00:54:20,120 --> 00:54:21,210
你是在哪里见到他的
Where did you meet him?

742
00:54:22,750 --> 00:54:24,960
是在出版纪念的后援会上
It was at a congratulatory reception for a book publication.

743
00:54:27,050 --> 00:54:29,470
当时你收到他的赞助费了吗
Did you receive a contribution from him at that time?

744
00:54:29,760 --> 00:54:32,220
我没能一一查看
I didn't have a chance to check every detail.

745
00:54:33,970 --> 00:54:35,720
所以没有办法回答你
So, I can't give you an answer.

746
00:54:43,810 --> 00:54:45,480
你见过这个人吗
Have you seen this man?

747
00:54:53,740 --> 00:54:57,290
金议员 你曾多次从崔基泰代表那里…
Mr. Kim, you have received cash from President Choi Kitae…

748
00:54:58,700 --> 00:55:02,290
收到过现金吧
on many occasions. Have you not?

749
00:55:03,710 --> 00:55:04,790
这个嘛
I'm not sure.

750
00:55:06,550 --> 00:55:08,380
我不记得我收过
I don't remember receiving any.

751
00:55:17,180 --> 00:55:18,680
我想你不用再回答了
I think you can stop now.

752
00:55:18,770 --> 00:55:20,770
应该也没什么可调查的了
I don't think there's anything more to investigate.

753
00:55:23,400 --> 00:55:24,940
这得问问千检察官
We should ask the prosecutor.

754
00:55:32,150 --> 00:55:33,240
他没说话 我们走吧
He says none. Let's go.

755
00:55:33,320 --> 00:55:35,570
不 我们休息一会儿再继续
No. We will take a short break and carry on.

756
00:55:37,830 --> 00:55:38,950
喂 千智勋
Hey, Cheon Jihun!

757
00:55:52,010 --> 00:55:55,010
透明 正直 开放的检察官
PROSECUTORS WITH TRANSPARENCY, INTEGRITY, OPENNESS

758
00:56:14,320 --> 00:56:15,530
这是什么
What is this?

759
00:56:16,490 --> 00:56:19,660
我想这是让你改变主意的唯一办法
I thought this was the only way to change your mind.

760
00:56:21,040 --> 00:56:22,330
你看看吧
Please take a look.

761
00:56:37,590 --> 00:56:40,390
你认为这样行得通吗
Do you think this will work?

762
00:56:40,930 --> 00:56:43,640
是的 我们等着瞧就知道了
Yes. I guess we will find out.

763
00:56:51,650 --> 00:56:53,320
如果他真的收了钱怎么办
What if he really took the money?

764
00:56:53,610 --> 00:56:56,360
千智勋这家伙虽然经常闯祸
Cheon Jihun causes a lot of trouble, but he's a good investigator.

765
00:56:56,450 --> 00:56:57,530
但他很擅长调查 不是吗
Cheon Jihun causes a lot of trouble, but he's a good investigator.

766
00:56:58,950 --> 00:57:01,200
他肯定是有线索才会这么做
He must be doing that because there is something.

767
00:57:01,290 --> 00:57:04,460
如果千检察官的话属实 我们得先下手为强
If what Jihun is saying is true, we need to make the first move.

768
00:57:04,540 --> 00:57:05,830
-什么 -什么
-What? -What?

769
00:57:06,420 --> 00:57:09,130
我刚接到几名议员的电话
I just received a few calls from some assemblymen.

770
00:57:09,210 --> 00:57:11,130
其中很多人惶恐不安
Many of them are nervous.

771
00:57:11,300 --> 00:57:12,170
我们该怎么办
What should we do?

772
00:57:12,880 --> 00:57:14,840
我们得给他们制定一个脱身策略
We have to get them an escape route.

773
00:57:15,630 --> 00:57:16,590
那么…
You mean…

774
00:57:17,220 --> 00:57:19,850
我们得让这案子定性成 金允燮议员单独受贿
We have to make it look like Kim Yoonsub took the money alone.

775
00:57:50,920 --> 00:57:54,170
我想这是让你改变主意的唯一办法
I thought this was the only way to change your mind.

776
00:58:07,730 --> 00:58:08,890
爸 你都听到了吧
Did you hear everything, Father?

777
00:58:10,190 --> 00:58:13,900
一旦开始调查 那些受贿之人全部会狡猾地脱身
When the investigations start, those who took the money will slip away,

778
00:58:15,190 --> 00:58:16,860
只剩下你一个人
and you will be left alone.

779
00:58:19,200 --> 00:58:23,780
而最终你将承担所有责任
Ultimately, you will take all of the blame.

780
00:58:24,410 --> 00:58:25,620
智勋
Jihun.

781
00:58:26,870 --> 00:58:28,250
我会帮你
I will help you.

782
00:58:29,960 --> 00:58:33,420
从现在开始纠正过来吧
You can correct it starting now.

783
00:59:05,200 --> 00:59:07,540
你转交给了几名议员
How many members of the Assembly did you give money to?

784
00:59:09,000 --> 00:59:10,000
有很多
There's a lot.

785
00:59:13,000 --> 00:59:15,670
我不知道你能否应付得了
I don't know if you can handle it.

786
00:59:21,630 --> 00:59:23,180
爸 你刚才不是听到了嘛
You heard it before, Father.

787
00:59:23,260 --> 00:59:25,350
我比你想象中
I am quite good at investigating,

788
00:59:26,220 --> 00:59:28,720
还要擅长调查
more than you think.

789
00:59:34,730 --> 00:59:37,940
我需要你转交钱财的证据
I need evidence that you delivered them the money.

790
00:59:39,480 --> 00:59:40,940
你手里有名单吧
I'm sure you have the list.

791
00:59:46,120 --> 00:59:47,120
我有
I do.

792
00:59:50,200 --> 00:59:51,830
我稍后给你名单
I will give you the list later.

793
00:59:55,210 --> 00:59:56,250
好
Fine.

794
00:59:56,340 --> 01:00:00,130
千智勋 检察官

795
01:00:07,100 --> 01:00:09,180
爸 我们今天就到此为止吧
Shall we stop for today, Father?

796
01:00:12,520 --> 01:00:13,690
可以吗
Can we do that?

797
01:00:14,900 --> 01:00:16,020
可以 当然了
Of course.

798
01:00:16,940 --> 01:00:19,360
首尔中央地方检察厅
SEOUL CENTRAL DISTRICT PROSECUTORS' OFFICE

799
01:00:27,030 --> 01:00:28,280
你回去吧
Go back in.

800
01:00:28,870 --> 01:00:30,410
不 我送你回去
I will take you home.

801
01:00:30,490 --> 01:00:33,910
不用 如果让别人看见了会说闲话
No. What will they say if they see us?

802
01:00:36,170 --> 01:00:38,090
好 我知道了
Yes, you're right.

803
01:00:38,670 --> 01:00:39,590
好
Okay.

804
01:00:43,170 --> 01:00:44,220
爸
Father.

805
01:00:49,680 --> 01:00:52,680
我曾想成为像你一样的检察官
I wanted to be a prosecutor just like you.

806
01:01:26,970 --> 01:01:28,180
简报

807
01:01:28,260 --> 01:01:31,100
上半年优秀检察官 首尔中央地检 千智勋
OUTSTANDING PROSECUTOR SEOUL CENTRAL DISTRICT'S CHEON JIHUN

808
01:02:04,800 --> 01:02:06,170
喂？我是千智勋
Yes, this is Cheon Jihun.

809
01:02:06,260 --> 01:02:09,300
千检察官 金议员的调查结束了吗
Mr. Cheon, is Mr. Kim done with the investigation?

810
01:02:09,380 --> 01:02:10,390
结束了
Yes.

811
01:02:11,640 --> 01:02:13,140
他下去有一会了
He went down a while ago.

812
01:02:13,760 --> 01:02:14,680
他还没出来吗
Has he not come out?

813
01:02:15,140 --> 01:02:18,850
是的 我在等他 但他不接电话
No. I'm waiting for him. He's not even answering his phone.

814
01:02:19,440 --> 01:02:21,150
好 我知道了 我下去看看
I understand. I'll head downstairs.

815
01:02:40,670 --> 01:02:43,500
千检察官 我去前门那边看看
Mr. Cheon, I will check the front gate!

816
01:02:43,590 --> 01:02:44,500
好
Okay.

817
01:02:47,380 --> 01:02:50,130
您拨打的电话暂时无人接听
The person you are calling cannot accept calls at this time.

818
01:02:50,220 --> 01:02:52,590
请稍后再拨
Please call back later.

819
01:03:14,490 --> 01:03:16,790
儿子
SON

820
01:04:35,200 --> 01:04:39,530
未知号码
RESTRICTED CALLER ID

821
01:04:48,880 --> 01:04:50,000
还没结束吗
Are you still in there?

822
01:04:51,710 --> 01:04:53,010
金允燮议员
Assemblyman Kim Yoonsub.

823
01:04:55,090 --> 01:04:56,130
你是谁
Who is this?

824
01:04:59,470 --> 01:05:00,430
你是谁
Who are you?

825
01:05:19,200 --> 01:05:21,910
《平价正义》
ONE DOLLAR LAWYER

826
01:06:04,120 --> 01:06:06,910
据说金允燮议员曾经 接受过检方调查 这是真的吗
Is it true that Assemblyman Kim was being investigated by prosecutors?

827
01:06:07,000 --> 01:06:08,370
负责的检察官是谁
Who was the prosecutor in charge?

828
01:06:08,460 --> 01:06:10,330
他们好像叫他瑞草洞疯狗
They say he's the mad dog of Seocho-dong.

829
01:06:10,420 --> 01:06:13,840
那种自以为 只有自己正义的人一定会闯祸
Those who act self-righteous always get themselves in trouble.

830
01:06:13,920 --> 01:06:15,670
那不是你的错
That wasn't your fault.

831
01:06:15,760 --> 01:06:17,090
他是我爸
He was my father.

832
01:06:17,420 --> 01:06:19,970
跟金允燮议员最后通话的 是一个非法登记的手机号
The number Assemblyman Kim spoke to on the phone was from a burner phone.

833
01:06:20,050 --> 01:06:21,760
我必须找到害死我爸的混蛋
I have to find the ones who did this to Father.

834
01:06:21,850 --> 01:06:22,680
你们就不要再深入调查了
Don't dig into it anymore.

835
01:06:22,760 --> 01:06:24,640
什么都不要做 就此放手
Don't do anything at all and pull out of it.

836
01:06:24,720 --> 01:06:26,730
我想要跟某个人一起共事
I found someone I want to work with.

837
01:06:26,810 --> 01:06:27,890
你来得正好
I'm so glad you're here.

838
01:06:27,980 --> 01:06:29,850
你一定会喜欢的
You'll absolutely love it.

839
01:06:29,940 --> 01:06:31,980
你看起来不像是来这里开咖啡馆的
You don't seem like the type to run a coffee house.

840
01:06:32,060 --> 01:06:33,400
你打算在这里做什么
What are you going to do here?

841
01:06:33,480 --> 01:06:35,690
这里是律师事务所吗
Is this the lawyer's office?

842
01:06:35,780 --> 01:06:37,280
那件事已经过去两年了
It has already been two years.

843
01:06:37,360 --> 01:06:38,990
你现在应该过自己的人生了吧
Shouldn't you live your own life now?

844
01:06:39,070 --> 01:06:41,950
不如你明天提交辞呈 然后来我的律所吧 怎么样
Why don't you resign tomorrow and join our office?